@startuml
title Viaverse Payment / Wallet — Activity Diagram
start
:QuoteAccepted;
:Validate accepted quote\nrequest owner / amount / state;
:Create PaymentSession\nidempotency key;
if (Saved card or checkout?) then (checkout)
  :Create provider checkout;
  :Receive provider callback;
else (saved token)
  :Use stored provider token;
endif
:Verify signature\namount / currency / state;
if (Valid + not duplicate?) then (yes)
  :Set PaymentAuthorized or Captured;
  :Calculate commission\n5% initial;
  :Create payout hold;
  :Emit PaymentAuthorized;
  :Emit CommissionCalculated;
  :Notify marketplace payment state update;
  :Job can continue;
else (no)
  :Mark payment failed;
  :Show retry path;
endif
stop

note bottom
Create session, provider callback, capture, refund and payout release must be idempotent.
Duplicate callbacks must not duplicate state changes.
end note
@enduml
